resources.string: Muat turun dan pasang ciri tambahan untuk View Cover LED. Anda boleh mencipta ikon LED anda sendiri dan tetapkannya sebagai ikon pemberitahuan anda. Untuk memuat turunnya kemudian, pergi ke Aturan > Ciri lanjutan > Aksesori > View cover LED, kemudian pilih Muat turun ciri tambahan.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
